      "raw_text": "taxpayers and members Of an organ\nization whose sole object is to protect\ntaxpayers as far as within our power,\ndo hereby appeal to the honorable\nlegislature of the State of Washington\nat their next regular session to repeal\nthe law and abolish entirely the office\nof road supervisor.\n\n\nRespectfully submitted,\n\n\nTAXPAYERS PROTECTIVE\n\n\nASSOCIATION.\n\n\nG. r. Cottrell, President.\n\n\nA. T. Rautinberg, Sec.\n\n\nDavid Mckenzie.\nThe resolution was forwarded to\nthe State Grange for ratification and\nwill be sent to other Oranges."
